    "ExtraInfo": "Usage Scenario\nThe display bfd bit-error-detection session command allows you to view information about BFD sessions for bit error detection. If a large number of BFD sessions for bit error detection exist, you can specify certain parameters to view only information about BFD sessions used to detect the bit errors of specific interfaces or LSPs.\nIf BFD sessions for bit error detection fail to be established, no information is displayed after you run this command."
